high_descs: Turn right, move to in front of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Turn left, move to the table.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the knife in the refrigerator.
Turn left, move to the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato form the table.
Turn right, move to in front the stove.
Put the slice of tomato in the pan on the right.
Pick up the pot, from the stove, containing the tomato slice.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the pot in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot containing a slice of tomato into the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn to face the sink.
Pick up the sharp knife with yellow handle from inside the sink.
Turn around and carry the knife to the brown table that will be on your right.
Use the knife to slice the tomato on the table that's next to the toaster.
Turn and carry the knife to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the knife on the second shelf on the right side.
Turn back around and move to the table where you just sliced the tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the table.
Turn right to move to the sink, then head right again to move to stand in front of the stove.
Place the tomato slice in the pot on the right side of the stove.
Pick up the pot with the tomato slice inside.
Turn and carry the pot and tomato slice to the fridge.
Place the pot with tomato slice inside on the top shelf on the right inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Refrigerate a tomato slice in a pot.

high_descs: Go to the sink
Pick up the knife
Go to the wooden table
Cut the tomato on the table
Go to the fridge
Put the knife in the fridge
Go to the wooden table
Pick up a tomato slice from the table
Go to the stove
Put the tomato in the pot
Pick up the pot
Go to the fridge
Put the pot in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and a pot with a tomato slice in it into the fridge
